{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "04", "m": "06", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "12", "M": "35", "S": "43"}}, "news": [{"title": "Develop 11 mega industrial parks, create 50,000-acre land bank: Bihar CM", "para": "Bihar's Chief Minister Samrat Choudhary has directed the development of 11 mega industrial parks and food parks in all 38 districts to boost industrial growth and employment. The state aims to create a land bank of 50,000 acres and simplify procedures to become an attractive investment destination, focusing on sectors like food processing and textiles.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/bihar-cm-announces-development-of-11-mega-industrial-parks-and-50000-acre-land-bank/131502074?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-1375654/131502074.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}, {"title": "Maharashtra government revises base rates under sand extraction policy", "para": "Maharashtra government has revised sand extraction policy, introducing new base rates and royalty for eco-friendly sand derived from mining by-products. This initiative aims to reduce pressure on riverbeds and encourage industries producing sand from overburden, while also curbing illegal excavation and supporting the construction sector.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/allied-industries/maharashtras-new-sand-extraction-policy-eco-friendly-rates-to-boost-construction-industry/131502357?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-187198/131502357.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "allied-industries"}, {"title": "UP-RERA says over 1.15 lakh units available across Uttar Pradesh", "para": "UP-RERA has advised homebuyers and investors to make property purchase decisions after verifying project details and assessing their financial capacity. The authority